snippet.title: Civium & The Problem Of Civilization w/ Jordan Hall (E47)
snippet.description:
A hopeful dialogue about the problem of civilization and what might be done about it. The first part is an introduction to the notion of Civium. The second part adds some paint to the canvas.

Consider supporting this project at https://www.patreon.com/voicecraft

Find conversation waypoints, more information, links to access and subscribe to the podcast @ https://wp.me/p2UC3z-G8

Find Jordan's ongoing Civium project playlist at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yXBAtdyBto0&list=PL4HY2aw0rBsS9hs9hw5fZi8jzLSEFW5fj
